{"id":5282,"date":"2024-01-29T09:38:26","date_gmt":"2020-01-29T04:08:26","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=5282"},"modified":"2024-02-09T14:49:29","modified_gmt":"2024-02-09T09:19:29","slug":"peaceful-study-room-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/study-room-interiors\/peaceful-study-room-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Sssshh! Here\u2019s A Great Mind At Work: Peaceful Study Room Designs!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Study rooms are spaces to get those billion dollar assignments going. Choose a design from our list to get cracking with ideas and inspiration.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\u2019re having difficulty completing your office tasks because of children running around or music blaring then it\u2019s time to get yourself a study room. A private home office where you can focus on your work. You do not need a large space for a study room. You can redesign a small space in your home and turn it into a study room, even if it&#8217;s in your bedroom. Regardless of the size or space, you can still design an affordable study room. Here are a bunch of smart study room designs for your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Peaceful Study Room Needs A Built-In Desk<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you space constraints then a built-in desk will do wonders. It is a real space saver. Depending on your spatial desires, you can design a desk with multiple drawers, shelves, and compartments to store documents. If you are someone who works a lot of the computer or uses equipment like audio jacks, microphones then opt for inexpensive hooks to hang them. From sleek single-occupant nooks to a fully equipped secretary style models, there is an array of built-in desk designs to keep you working with endless ease. A right built-in desk will keep you in good stead with style, no matter the task at hand.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003919\/peaceful-study-room-built-in-desk.jpg\" alt=\"Peaceful study room with a built-in desk to make the best study room design\" class=\"wp-image-5283\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003919\/peaceful-study-room-built-in-desk.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003919\/peaceful-study-room-built-in-desk-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003919\/peaceful-study-room-built-in-desk-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003919\/peaceful-study-room-built-in-desk-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A built-in desk is a statement of cool and space saver<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Study room designs to maximise productivity and focus!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/09142912\/study-room-designs-to-maximise-productivity-and-focus.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Pinch Of Motivation For Peaceful Study<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Where do you normally work? If the answer is lying on your bed with a laptop munching on crisps, then you might want to reconsider revamping your study space. The time you spend on your work should be conducive. To achieve your goal, hang a motivational board, pictures, and messages to give you a booster shot of inspiration. Daily reminder of your goals and dreams are a great starting point! You can be absolutely creative, colourful or laid back. Install a blackboard where you can scribble motivational quotes to stay inspired. Build an aura in your study room that will bring you closer to achieving your goals.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003925\/home-study-room-design-motivational-quotes.jpg\" alt=\"Home study room design with a motivational quotes in your study room, it will inspire you\" class=\"wp-image-5285\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003925\/home-study-room-design-motivational-quotes.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003925\/home-study-room-design-motivational-quotes-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003925\/home-study-room-design-motivational-quotes-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003925\/home-study-room-design-motivational-quotes-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Motivational quotes in your study room will inspire you more<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Bookwheel Is Cool And A Space Saver Too<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\u2019re seeking a clever way to declutter and organise your mountain of prized books, do it in a unique manner. A book wheel lends an interesting look to your study room and creates more than enough storage room. A pile of books, paper, clothing or other items will affect your ability to study. As a matter of fact, it will change your mood from studying to cleaning. Decluttering and re-organising your space will help you eliminate distractions before you dedicate your time and energy to studying. Thus a book wheel in your study room will help you achieve the same.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003928\/peaceful-study-room-design-bookwheel.jpg\" alt=\"Peaceful study room design with a bookwheel is cool and a space saver as well\" class=\"wp-image-5287\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003928\/peaceful-study-room-design-bookwheel.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003928\/peaceful-study-room-design-bookwheel-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003928\/peaceful-study-room-design-bookwheel-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003928\/peaceful-study-room-design-bookwheel-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Keeping your study room clutter-free will help you concentrate more<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Modern Space Saving Study Table | Study Table Design | DesignCafe\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/321jB4bKrRA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Don\u2019t Study In The Dark<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Good lighting is an essential feature for study rooms. Never study or work in a dimly-lit room as it encourages sleep. Make sure the lights in your study are bright enough to clearly read books or work on your computer without extra effort be it morning, noon or night. A stylish table lamp can fit any specifications for both functionality and style. Consider adding LED lamps on your desk to brighten things up. You can opt for pendant lighting because of its flexibility and contemporary aesthetics. It gives you direct light and is sturdy as it\u2019s fastened to the ceiling. It saves spaces on your desk for that pile of books you wanted to read.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003934\/peaceful-study-room-design-pendant-lights.jpg\" alt=\"Peaceful study room design by adding pendant lights will provide good lighting\" class=\"wp-image-5289\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003934\/peaceful-study-room-design-pendant-lights.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003934\/peaceful-study-room-design-pendant-lights-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003934\/peaceful-study-room-design-pendant-lights-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003934\/peaceful-study-room-design-pendant-lights-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Adding pendant lights will provide good lighting plus adds a fashion statement to your study room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Ergonomic study room interiors perfect for indian homes\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/15154220\/ergonomic-study-room-interiors-perfect-for-indian-homes-scaled.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Enchant Your Study Room With These Colours<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Colours play a vital role when it comes to designing a peaceful study room. Certain shades are better choices where studying and achieving tasks becomes simpler as if affects the mood in a positive manner. Opt for <strong><em>deep grey silver<\/em><\/strong> as it promotes creativity and helps you focus tasks at hand. <strong><em>Blue <\/em><\/strong>is a calm and soothing colour that promotes productivity. A brighter shade of blue will help you focus and engage better. For the right amount of concentration, <strong><em>green<\/em><\/strong> is the ideal colour. Try fresh sage or moss-green so it doesn\u2019t overpower your study room. If you have the habit of dozing off then a coat of<strong> <em>red<\/em><\/strong> will boost your energy if you\u2019re a night owl. Try muted colours like brick, wine or maroon and you\u2019re all set to burn the midnight oil.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003936\/peaceful-study-room-design-with-colours.jpg\" alt=\"Peaceful best study room design with colours like brick, wine or maroon\" class=\"wp-image-5290\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003936\/peaceful-study-room-design-with-colours.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003936\/peaceful-study-room-design-with-colours-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003936\/peaceful-study-room-design-with-colours-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003936\/peaceful-study-room-design-with-colours-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Pick a paintbrush and give your study room a brand-new look<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Don\u2019t Keep Your Walls Empty<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Artwork is important! Turn empty walls into a vision board. Transform those boring walls into a space to focus on things you want, places you want to travel to and inspirational ways to live life. Place neat artwork like your favourite painting or a wall calendar. A chalkboard calendar will make the wall functional&nbsp; and neat! A bulletin board will help you keep clutter away from the desk and turn a messy office into a masterpiece.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003939\/peaceful-study-room-wall-decor.jpg\" alt=\"Peaceful study room design with the right amount of decor and creativity\" class=\"wp-image-5291\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003939\/peaceful-study-room-wall-decor.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003939\/peaceful-study-room-wall-decor-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003939\/peaceful-study-room-wall-decor-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003939\/peaceful-study-room-wall-decor-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Empty walls can be turned into a masterpiece with the right amount of decor and creativity<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/study-room-interiors\/latest-study-room-interior-design-ideas\/\">Study room interior design<\/a> does not need to be a boring affair. These clever interior designs can make your study room a place to get things done. It may feel like an unachievable project but with careful strategy and planning, your study room will inspire you everyday! By utilising natural lights, refurbished furniture, and clever organisational techniques, you can turn your study time into fun time. Design Cafe has an arsenal of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">professional designers<\/a> to help you plan and execute the perfect study room for your children or yourself. Call us now!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/diy-study-space-ideas\/\">DIY Study Space Ideas For Your Home<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/study-room-interiors\/study-ideas-compact-homes\/\">Study Ideas For Compact Homes<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Productive Spaces For An Ideal Home<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Smart modular solutions for Indian homes<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06164015\/91.png\"\n                    selected>\n                    +91\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+44\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163955\/44.png\">\n                    +44\n                <\/option>\n                <